# Pre-submission checklist

## Backend
[ ] All routes return JSON errors (no HTML 500 pages)
[ ] File cleanup: delete temp uploads after transcription
[ ] MONGO_URI, API keys set in production env
[ ] CORS origins updated to prod frontend URL
[ ] No console.log in production (use a logger or NODE_ENV guard)

## Frontend
[ ] VITE_API_URL set in Netlify/Vercel environment
[ ] Loading + error states on every async action
[ ] ErrorBoundary wraps the app root
[ ] Auth redirects work on page reload
[ ] Mobile responsive (tested on 375px)

## Cleanup
[ ] Remove all console.log / debugger statements
[ ] .env files in .gitignore
[ ] node_modules in .gitignore
[ ] uploads/ folder in .gitignore